column2: SELECT m.id as [id], str (m.ra, #, #) AS ra, str (m.dec, #, #) AS dec, sp.plate, sp.fiberid, sp.mjd, sp.z, sp.zwarning, g.Flux_Hb_#, g.Flux_Hb_#_Err, g.Flux_OIII_#, g.Flux_OIII_#_Err, g.Flux_OI_#, g.Flux_OI_#_Err, g.Flux_SII_#, g.Flux_SII_#_Err, g.Flux_SII_#, g.Flux_SII_#_Err, g.Flux_NII_#, g.Flux_NII_#_Err, g.Flux_OII_#, g.Flux_OII_#_Err, g.Flux_OII_#, g.Flux_OII_#_Err, g.Flux_Ha_#, g.Flux_Ha_#_Err, g.bpt into mydb.listMgIIphot_t2 from MyDB.listMgIIphot AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON n.objID = sp.objID LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specobjID = sp.specobjID LEFT OUTER JOIN emissionLinesPort as g ON g.specobjID = sp.specobjID JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID = sp.objID WHERE (sp.z > = #) OR (pz.z > = #) ORDER by m.id
